flowRoot.flowPara: Ever felt lost and unsure of what modules to take in NUS? Fret not, NUS Timetable System (NUTS) is here to help you! NUTS is an expert system designed to help students plan their modules and timetable according to their degree requirements.
NUTS will auto generate an ideal timetable with no module or exam clashes.
The system will generate modules that satisfy prerequisite and preclusion
Hate science? Love artificial intelligence? Indicate these preferences to NUTS and it will use its own scoring system to help you select your modules!
